  "body": "### Steps to reproduce:\r\n1. Be a member of a group chat.\r\n2. Receive a regular message in the group chat.\r\n3. Check the display of the unread indicator on the chat tab\r\n\r\n### Actual result:\r\nThe unread counter is shown instead of an unread badge for non-mention messages in the group chat and chat tab\r\n![image](https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/52490791/9e5c6c95-ff09-4309-ad40-06671b128026)\r\n\r\n### Expected result:\r\nAn unread badge should be displayed instead of the unread counter for regular (non-mention and non-reply) messages in the chat tab\r\n\r\nDiscussed with design team https://discord.com/channels/624634427930312714/928646594314784859/1129000866406477835\r\n![image](https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/52490791/e3f3117c-cafb-4703-a103-ee495e94f995)\r\n\r\n### ENV:\r\n - Nightly [28 Sep 2023]",
